{"tid":397213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係廢老] 頭先搭地鐵有廢老行埋黎眼神示意叫我讓位","createTime":"2017-09-12T10:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T11:20:53.000Z","uid":145117,"like":208,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afa5653017718d38e7f8825062e0e5556f343eb3","tid":397213,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小妹頭先搭西鐵綫 係屯門有上車 所以有位坐都好正常 去到天水圍站 有位目測六旬既婦人衝左上車 然後九秒九行去企我前邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  眼神示意叫我讓位比佢/比佢老公 <br />\n心諗妳唔似有需要我讓喎 所以我冇理到 然而我隔離2個姨姨就似乎比佢既眼神嚇蛭 彈左起身讓位比對廢老 但個婦人唔該都無聲就坐低左 反而佢老公都有講聲唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個婦人坐低之後仲要大大聲講電話 我真係寧願坐住係到先 留個位比其他有需要既人好過<br />\n<br />\nBtw而家d廢老真係越黎越得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打做得啱 縱容廢老既行為真係不可一 不可再<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家d後生連尊重同關懷老人家都唔識"},{"pid":"3e68a73ab84e58744cbe34e60abb2464f75013b8","tid":397213,"uid":137503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7b29ae512a2235e9a30b63450d9f5d0723680e","tid":397213,"uid":145117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔可以太縱容d廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e041f717b6ffcda4bf78a07b45863e523c41ac1","tid":397213,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d老野真無當自己有特權"},{"pid":"6f7d1a08c3b6c82413d06eb050216151fd588cf9","tid":397213,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"叫你拉反褲鏈